<h2>Thermostat Dial — Which arc style?</h2>
<p class="subtitle">Three approaches to fitting a dial into the existing card grid</p>

<div class="cards">

  <!-- Option A: Full circular dial -->
  <div class="card" data-choice="a" onclick="toggleSelect(this)">
    <div class="card-image" style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:220px;">
      <div style="position:relative;width:160px;height:160px;">
        <svg width="160" height="160" viewBox="0 0 160 160">
          <!-- track -->
          <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="64" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff18" stroke-width="12" stroke-dasharray="380 21" stroke-dashoffset="-10" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <!-- fill (60%) -->
          <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="64" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="12" stroke-dasharray="228 173" stroke-dashoffset="-10" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <!-- knob -->
          <circle cx="80" cy="16" r="8" fill="#f59e0b" transform="rotate(216 80 80)"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;">
          <span style="font-size:11px;opacity:.5;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase">current</span>
          <span style="font-size:32px;font-weight:700;line-height:1">71°</span>
          <span style="font-size:12px;color:#f59e0b;">→ 72°</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:12px;color:#ffffff60;">Living Room · Heat</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3>Full Ring</h3>
      <p>Full circle, drag the knob around the ring to set target temp. Needs <code>col-span-2</code> width. Classic Nest feel.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Option B: Bottom arc (gauge) -->
  <div class="card" data-choice="b" onclick="toggleSelect(this)">
    <div class="card-image" style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:24px 24px 8px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:220px;">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;margin-bottom:4px;">
        <span style="font-size:40px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;">71°</span>
        <span style="font-size:14px;color:#f59e0b;">→ 72°</span>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#ffffff40;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:12px;">LIVING ROOM · HEAT</div>
      <div style="position:relative;width:200px;height:108px;overflow:hidden;">
        <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200" style="margin-top:-92px;">
          <!-- track -->
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="88" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff15" stroke-width="14" stroke-dasharray="276 276" stroke-dashoffset="0" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(180 100 100)"/>
          <!-- fill (55%) -->
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="88" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="14" stroke-dasharray="152 400" stroke-dashoffset="0" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(180 100 100)"/>
          <!-- knob -->
          <circle cx="100" cy="12" r="9" fill="#f59e0b" transform="rotate(99 100 100)"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:2px;left:0;right:0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 8px;font-size:10px;color:#ffffff40;">
          <span>60°</span><span>85°</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3>Bottom Arc (Gauge)</h3>
      <p>Half-circle arc at the bottom like a speedometer. Compact vertically, works at <code>col-span-2</code>. Natural temp range left→right.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Option C: Compact arc inline -->
  <div class="card" data-choice="c" onclick="toggleSelect(this)">
    <div class="card-image" style="background:#1a1a2e;padding:20px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;min-height:220px;justify-content:center;">
      <!-- header row -->
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:#ffffff40;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:2px;">Living Room</div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:6px;">
            <span style="font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;">71°</span>
            <span style="font-size:13px;color:#f59e0b;">→ 72°</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:right;">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:#f59e0b;letter-spacing:.05em;">HEAT</div>
          <div style="margin-top:6px;display:flex;gap:6px;">
            <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;background:#ffffff12;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;">−</div>
            <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;background:#f59e0b;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#000;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;">+</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- arc progress bar -->
      <div style="position:relative;height:40px;">
        <svg width="100%" height="80" viewBox="0 0 300 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="position:absolute;top:-20px;">
          <path d="M 20 70 A 130 130 0 0 1 280 70" fill="none" stroke="#ffffff12" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M 20 70 A 130 130 0 0 1 280 70" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="360" stroke-dashoffset="162"/>
          <circle cx="190" cy="22" r="7" fill="#f59e0b"/>
        </svg>
        <div style="position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:10px;color:#ffffff30;padding:0 4px;">
          <span>60°</span><span>85°</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h3>Compact Arc Strip</h3>
      <p>Flat arc at the bottom of a standard card. Keeps the half-width grid cell, adds arc for visual feedback. +/− buttons for adjusting. Most space-efficient.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
